El '''evento festivo 2025''' es un evento comunitario para celebrar la [[Wikipedia:Christmas_and_holiday_season|temporada navideña y festividades]] de 2025. El evento presenta contenido invernal en la [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|tienda]], una campaña de regalos y varias recompensas para los usuarios que participen. Se lleva a cabo del 8 de diciembre de 2025 al 1 de enero de 2026.

<span id="Holiday_Event"></span>
==Evento festivo==
[[File:HolidayEvent2025 VRC+Page.png|thumb|Captura de pantalla del menú del evento festivo de 2025]]
El evento festivo es una campaña de regalos comunitarios para la temporada festiva.

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Users can participate and track progress by navigating to the Holiday Event tab in the VRC+ page on the Main Menu. By participating in the campaign, users earn several rewards, such as exclusive inventory content and a badge for completing the event.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">The campaign began at 11:40PM UTC on December 8th, 2025 and ends at 7:59:59AM UTC on January 1st, 2026.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">===Leaderboards===</span>
<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Users that have participated in the event by gifting can appear on the top gifters leaderboard. The "2025 Holiday Heros" leaderboard section is spilt up between global and friends. Both lists will show the top 10 gifters, and the top three users will have different stages of holiday wreaths applied to their profile picture.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Users can choose to "Appear as Anonymous" to anonymize their username appearing on the global and friends list.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">===Rewards===</span>
<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">The following rewards can be obtained from this event:</span>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Festive Starter Pack
** Available to everyone
** "[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|Festive Starter Pack]]" bundle
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* The First Gift
** Available to users who gifted one VRC+ subscription or Shop gift.
</div><ref name="CreditsPurchase" group="note"><span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Purchasing VRChat Credits counts towards gift count.</span></ref>
** <span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">"[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|Tree-in-a-Box]]" Premium [[Special:MyLanguage/Emojis|emoji]]</span>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* VRC+ Gifter
** Available to users who gifted one VRC+ subscription.
</div><ref name="CreditsPurchase" group="note" />
** <span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">"[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles & Packs|VRC+ Gifter]]" bundle</span>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Holiday Legend
** Available to users who gifted five VRC+ subscriptions or Shop gifts.<ref name="CreditsPurchase" group="note" />
** "Wrapped Up!" [[Special:MyLanguage/Warp Effects|warp effect]]
